	Easy to install
</h3>
<p>Simply <a href="https://docs.gitea.io/en-us/install-from-binary/">run the binary</a> for your platform, ship it with <a href="https://docs.gitea.io/en-us/install-with-docker/">Docker</a>, or get it <a href="https://docs.gitea.io/en-us/install-from-package/">packaged</a>.</p>

